description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 25

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The weakest group from the MKR Food Truck must fight to stay in the competition in an intense cook-off where they will be using ingredients from the fridge of a stranger. The weakest team heads to Sudden Death against Carly and Tresne.
